Who's News:
   Bridgestone Appoints
   Uchiyama Sales Head
   At Its U.S. Tire Unit
The tire operations, based in Nashville, Tenn., also named
to its board Sunil Kumar, 42, executive vice president-retail
operations, and G.B. Pazos, 58, executive vice
president-South America operations. The appointments of
Messrs. Uchiyama, Kumar and Pazos to the board fill vacancies
left by Mr. Ogden and Akihiro Ono, who will remain executive
vice president of Bridgestone, and increases the size of the
board to seven from six.